'''席歐多·彼得·詹姆斯·金奈爾德·泰提李斯'''（{{lang-en|Theodore Peter James Kinnaird Taptiklis}}，<ref name=birth>''Births, Marriages & Deaths Index of England & Wales, 1916–2005''. Ancestry.com</ref>{{bd|1984年|12月16日||}}）<ref name="Nottingham1">Staff (23 April 2010). [http://www.alumni.nottingham.ac.uk/NetCommunity/Page.aspx?pid=1705 "New Theatre Graduates Star in Blockbuster TV Roles"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141106060057/http://www.alumni.nottingham.ac.uk/NetCommunity/Page.aspx?pid=1705 |date=2014-11-06 }}. [[University_of_Nottingham|University of Nottingham]]; retrieved 27 February 2013.</ref><ref name="SkyLiving1">Staff (23 January 2011).  [http://skyliving.sky.com/biog-theo-james "Biog: Theo James"] {{Wayback|url=http://skyliving.sky.com/biog-theo-james |date=20111219202554 }}. [[Sky_Living|Sky Living]]. Retrieved 27 February 2013.</ref>或簡稱'''席歐·詹姆斯'''（{{lang-en|Theo James}}）是一位[[英国|英国]]男演员，以饰演《{{link-en|鬼影喧囂|Bedlam (2011 TV series)}}》中的杰德·哈珀（Jed Harper）出名。

2013年，詹姆斯在[[哥伦比亚广播公司|哥伦比亚广播公司]]犯罪剧《[[警界金童|警界金童]]》中领衔主演一个新秀侦探和未来的[[纽约市|纽约市]]警察局长小沃尔特·威廉·克拉克（Walter William Clark, Jr.）。2014年，他在[[韦罗妮卡·罗思|韦罗妮卡·罗思]]的小说改编的电影《[[分歧者系列電影|分歧者系列電影]]》中扮演男主角托比亞·「四號」·伊頓（Tobias "Four" Eaton）。

詹姆斯除表演外，还在伦敦一个乐队「Shere Khan」担任歌手和吉他手。<ref>{{cite web|last=Deming|first=Mark|title=Theo James to Star in ‘Divergent’: Five Things to Know About Him|url=https://movies.yahoo.com/blogs/movie-talk/five-things-theo-james-201334739.html|publisher=[[Yahoo|Yahoo]]|accessdate=2 April 2014|date=15 March 2013|archive-date=2014-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140416041658/https://movies.yahoo.com/blogs/movie-talk/five-things-theo-james-201334739.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2012年11月21日，乐队在他们的[[Facebook|Facebook]]上宣布将各自发展音乐事业。<ref>{{cite web|last=Jones|first=Nate|title=Sexy Man Sing-Off! Divergent's Theo James & 8 More Actor-Crooners|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20800088,00.html|publisher=People|date=26 March 2014|access-date=2014-04-14|archive-date=2016-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160418025900/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20800088,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==早年和教育==
詹姆斯出生在英国牛津郡牛津，父母是Jane (née Martin)和菲利普·塔普蒂克利斯（Philip Taptiklis）。<ref>Young, Susan (9 September 2011). [http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118042124 {{Wayback|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118042124 |date=20120313173545 }} "James' 'Stranger' Role Leads to 'Bedlam'{{spaced ndash}} TV's Top 10: New Faces for Fall{{spaced ndash}} Theo James". ''[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]''; retrieved 27 February 2013.</ref><ref>Staff (25 January 2011). [http://announcements.thetimes.co.uk/obituaries/timesonline-uk/obituary-preview.aspx?n=barbara-taptiklis&pid=152188637&referrer=2282 "Barbara Taptiklis Obituary"] {{Wayback|url=http://announcements.thetimes.co.uk/obituaries/timesonline-uk/obituary-preview.aspx?n=barbara-taptiklis&pid=152188637&referrer=2282 |date=20150929224833 }} (preview). ''[[The_Times|The Times]]''; retrieved 27 February 2013.</ref>他的祖父是希腊人（从伯罗奔尼撒移居新西兰）。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.espressonews.gr/%CF%80%CE%B5%CF%81%CE%B9%CE%B5%CF%87%CF%8C%CE%BC%CE%B5%CE%BD%CE%BF/63003/%CE%B5%CF%87%CF%89-%CF%87%CE%AC%CF%83%CE%B5%CE%B9-%CF%84%CE%BF%CE%BD-%CF%8D%CF%80%CE%BD%CE%BF-%CE%BC%CE%BF%CF%85-%CE%B3%CE%B9%CE%B1-%CF%84%CE%B7%CE%BD-%CE%B5%CE%BB%CE%B5%CE%BD%CE%B7 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304062821/http://www.espressonews.gr/%CF%80%CE%B5%CF%81%CE%B9%CE%B5%CF%87%CF%8C%CE%BC%CE%B5%CE%BD%CE%BF/63003/%CE%B5%CF%87%CF%89-%CF%87%CE%AC%CF%83%CE%B5%CE%B9-%CF%84%CE%BF%CE%BD-%CF%8D%CF%80%CE%BD%CE%BF-%CE%BC%CE%BF%CF%85-%CE%B3%CE%B9%CE%B1-%CF%84%CE%B7%CE%BD-%CE%B5%CE%BB%CE%B5%CE%BD%CE%B7 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>他祖先原是英格兰人和苏格兰人。<ref name=thestar1>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/television/2013/03/07/theo_james_leapt_at_chance_to_play_tough_new_york_cop_in_golden_boy.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2014-04-14 |archive-date=2017-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170925035502/https://www.thestar.com/entertainment/television/2013/03/07/theo_james_leapt_at_chance_to_play_tough_new_york_cop_in_golden_boy.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>提奥有两个哥哥和两个姐姐，他是五个孩子中最小的一个。<ref name=thestar1/><ref>{{cite web|last=Topel|first=Fred|title=Theo James Talks Bedlam|url=http://www.craveonline.com/tv/interviews/175884-theo-james-talks-bedlam|work=CraveOnline|accessdate=10 December 2013|date=10 October 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141113063102/http://www.craveonline.com/tv/interviews/175884-theo-james-talks-bedlam|archive-date=2014-11-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>他入读{{link-en|艾爾斯伯里文法學校|Aylesbury Grammar School}}，在[[诺丁汉大学|诺丁汉大学]]获得了哲学学士学位。他在{{link-en|布里斯托尔老维克剧院学校|Bristol Old Vic Theatre School}}学习表演。<ref name="Nottingham1"/><ref name="SkyLiving1"/>

